{"response":{"verses":[{"auditid":"0","verse":"1","lastverse":"1","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.14.1","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Cor.14.1","label":"","reference":"1 Corinthiens 14:1","prev_osis_id":"1Cor.013.013,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Cor.014.002,fra-LSG","text":"<h3 class=\"s\">Comparaison entre le don des langues et le don de proph\u00e9tie<\/h3>\n<h5 class=\"r\">V. 1-40: cf. 1 Co 12:4-7, 27-31. Ro 14:19. 1 Pi 4:10, 11.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Cor.14.1\" class=\"v\">1<\/sup>Recherchez la charit\u00e9. Aspirez aussi aux dons spirituels, mais surtout \u00e0 celui de proph\u00e9tie.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Cor.14","name":"1 Corinthiens 14","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.14"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Cor.14.2","name":"1 Corinthiens 14:2","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.14.2"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Cor.13.13","name":"1 Corinthiens 13:13","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.13.13"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"2","lastverse":"2","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.14.2","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Cor.14.2","label":"","reference":"1 Corinthiens 14:2","prev_osis_id":"1Cor.014.001,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Cor.014.003,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Cor.14.2\" class=\"v\">2<\/sup>En effet, celui qui parle en langue ne parle pas aux hommes, mais \u00e0 Dieu, car personne ne le comprend, et c\u2019est en esprit qu\u2019il dit des myst\u00e8res.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Cor.14","name":"1 Corinthiens 14","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.14"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Cor.14.3","name":"1 Corinthiens 14:3","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.14.3"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Cor.14.1","name":"1 Corinthiens 14:1","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.14.1"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"3","lastverse":"3","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.14.3","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Cor.14.3","label":"","reference":"1 Corinthiens 14:3","prev_osis_id":"1Cor.014.002,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Cor.014.004,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Cor.14.3\" class=\"v\">3<\/sup>Celui qui proph\u00e9tise, au contraire, parle aux hommes, les \u00e9difie, les exhorte, les console.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Cor.14","name":"1 Corinthiens 14","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.14"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Cor.14.4","name":"1 Corinthiens 14:4","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.14.4"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Cor.14.2","name":"1 Corinthiens 14:2","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.14.2"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"4","lastverse":"4","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.14.4","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Cor.14.4","label":"","reference":"1 Corinthiens 14:4","prev_osis_id":"1Cor.014.003,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Cor.014.005,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Cor.14.4\" class=\"v\">4<\/sup>Celui qui parle en langue s\u2019\u00e9difie lui-m\u00eame; celui qui proph\u00e9tise \u00e9difie l\u2019\u00c9glise.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Cor.14","name":"1 Corinthiens 14","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.14"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Cor.14.5","name":"1 Corinthiens 14:5","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.14.5"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Cor.14.3","name":"1 Corinthiens 14:3","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.14.3"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"5","lastverse":"5","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.14.5","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Cor.14.5","label":"","reference":"1 Corinthiens 14:5","prev_osis_id":"1Cor.014.004,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Cor.014.006,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Cor.14.5\" class=\"v\">5<\/sup>Je d\u00e9sire que vous parliez tous en langues, mais encore plus que vous proph\u00e9tisiez. Celui qui proph\u00e9tise est plus grand que celui qui parle en langues, \u00e0 moins que ce dernier n\u2019interpr\u00e8te, pour que l\u2019\u00c9glise en re\u00e7oive de l\u2019\u00e9dification.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Cor.14","name":"1 Corinthiens 14","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.14"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Cor.14.6","name":"1 Corinthiens 14:6","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.14.6"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Cor.14.4","name":"1 Corinthiens 14:4","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.14.4"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"6","lastverse":"6","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.14.6","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Cor.14.6","label":"","reference":"1 Corinthiens 14:6","prev_osis_id":"1Cor.014.005,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Cor.014.007,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Cor.14.6\" class=\"v\">6<\/sup>Et maintenant, fr\u00e8res, de quelle utilit\u00e9 vous serais-je, si je venais \u00e0 vous parlant en langues, et si je ne vous parlais pas par r\u00e9v\u00e9lation, ou par connaissance, ou par proph\u00e9tie, ou par doctrine?<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Cor.14","name":"1 Corinthiens 14","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.14"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Cor.14.7","name":"1 Corinthiens 14:7","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.14.7"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Cor.14.5","name":"1 Corinthiens 14:5","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.14.5"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"7","lastverse":"7","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.14.7","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Cor.14.7","label":"","reference":"1 Corinthiens 14:7","prev_osis_id":"1Cor.014.006,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Cor.014.008,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Cor.14.7\" class=\"v\">7<\/sup>Si les objets inanim\u00e9s qui rendent un son, comme une fl\u00fbte ou une harpe, ne rendent pas des sons distincts, comment reconna\u00eetra-t-on ce qui est jou\u00e9 sur la fl\u00fbte ou sur la harpe?<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Cor.14","name":"1 Corinthiens 14","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.14"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Cor.14.8","name":"1 Corinthiens 14:8","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.14.8"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Cor.14.6","name":"1 Corinthiens 14:6","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.14.6"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"8","lastverse":"8","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.14.8","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Cor.14.8","label":"","reference":"1 Corinthiens 14:8","prev_osis_id":"1Cor.014.007,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Cor.014.009,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Cor.14.8\" class=\"v\">8<\/sup>Et si la trompette rend un son confus, qui se pr\u00e9parera au combat?<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Cor.14","name":"1 Corinthiens 14","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.14"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Cor.14.9","name":"1 Corinthiens 14:9","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.14.9"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Cor.14.7","name":"1 Corinthiens 14:7","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.14.7"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"9","lastverse":"9","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.14.9","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Cor.14.9","label":"","reference":"1 Corinthiens 14:9","prev_osis_id":"1Cor.014.008,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Cor.014.010,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Cor.14.9\" class=\"v\">9<\/sup>De m\u00eame vous, si par la langue vous ne donnez pas une parole distincte, comment saura-t-on ce que vous dites? Car vous parlerez en l\u2019air.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Cor.14","name":"1 Corinthiens 14","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.14"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Cor.14.10","name":"1 Corinthiens 14:10","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.14.10"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Cor.14.8","name":"1 Corinthiens 14:8","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.14.8"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"10","lastverse":"10","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.14.10","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Cor.14.10","label":"","reference":"1 Corinthiens 14:10","prev_osis_id":"1Cor.014.009,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Cor.014.011,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Cor.14.10\" class=\"v\">10<\/sup>Quelque nombreuses que puissent \u00eatre dans le monde les diverses langues, il n\u2019en est aucune qui ne soit une langue intelligible;<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Cor.14","name":"1 Corinthiens 14","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.14"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Cor.14.11","name":"1 Corinthiens 14:11","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.14.11"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Cor.14.9","name":"1 Corinthiens 14:9","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.14.9"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"11","lastverse":"11","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.14.11","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Cor.14.11","label":"","reference":"1 Corinthiens 14:11","prev_osis_id":"1Cor.014.010,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Cor.014.012,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Cor.14.11\" class=\"v\">11<\/sup>si donc je ne connais pas le sens de la langue, je serai un barbare pour celui qui parle, et celui qui parle sera un barbare pour moi.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Cor.14","name":"1 Corinthiens 14","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.14"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Cor.14.12","name":"1 Corinthiens 14:12","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.14.12"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Cor.14.10","name":"1 Corinthiens 14:10","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.14.10"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"12","lastverse":"12","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.14.12","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Cor.14.12","label":"","reference":"1 Corinthiens 14:12","prev_osis_id":"1Cor.014.011,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Cor.014.013,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Cor.14.12\" class=\"v\">12<\/sup>De m\u00eame vous, puisque vous aspirez aux dons spirituels, que ce soit pour l\u2019\u00e9dification de l\u2019\u00c9glise que vous cherchiez \u00e0 en poss\u00e9der abondamment.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Cor.14","name":"1 Corinthiens 14","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.14"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Cor.14.13","name":"1 Corinthiens 14:13","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.14.13"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Cor.14.11","name":"1 Corinthiens 14:11","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.14.11"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"13","lastverse":"13","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.14.13","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Cor.14.13","label":"","reference":"1 Corinthiens 14:13","prev_osis_id":"1Cor.014.012,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Cor.014.014,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Cor.14.13\" class=\"v\">13<\/sup>C\u2019est pourquoi, que celui qui parle en langue prie pour avoir le don d\u2019interpr\u00e9ter.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Cor.14","name":"1 Corinthiens 14","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.14"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Cor.14.14","name":"1 Corinthiens 14:14","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.14.14"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Cor.14.12","name":"1 Corinthiens 14:12","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.14.12"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"14","lastverse":"14","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.14.14","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Cor.14.14","label":"","reference":"1 Corinthiens 14:14","prev_osis_id":"1Cor.014.013,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Cor.014.015,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Cor.14.14\" class=\"v\">14<\/sup>Car si je prie en langue, mon esprit est en pri\u00e8re, mais mon intelligence demeure st\u00e9rile.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Cor.14","name":"1 Corinthiens 14","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.14"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Cor.14.15","name":"1 Corinthiens 14:15","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.14.15"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Cor.14.13","name":"1 Corinthiens 14:13","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.14.13"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"15","lastverse":"15","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.14.15","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Cor.14.15","label":"","reference":"1 Corinthiens 14:15","prev_osis_id":"1Cor.014.014,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Cor.014.016,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Cor.14.15\" class=\"v\">15<\/sup>Que faire donc? Je prierai par l\u2019esprit, mais je prierai aussi avec l\u2019intelligence; je chanterai par l\u2019esprit, mais je chanterai aussi avec l\u2019intelligence.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Cor.14","name":"1 Corinthiens 14","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.14"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Cor.14.16","name":"1 Corinthiens 14:16","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.14.16"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Cor.14.14","name":"1 Corinthiens 14:14","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.14.14"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"16","lastverse":"16","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.14.16","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Cor.14.16","label":"","reference":"1 Corinthiens 14:16","prev_osis_id":"1Cor.014.015,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Cor.014.017,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Cor.14.16\" class=\"v\">16<\/sup>Autrement, si tu rends gr\u00e2ces par l\u2019esprit, comment celui qui est dans les rangs de l\u2019homme du peuple r\u00e9pondra-t-il Amen! \u00c0 ton action de gr\u00e2ces, puisqu\u2019il ne sait pas ce que tu dis?<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Cor.14","name":"1 Corinthiens 14","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.14"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Cor.14.17","name":"1 Corinthiens 14:17","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.14.17"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Cor.14.15","name":"1 Corinthiens 14:15","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.14.15"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"17","lastverse":"17","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.14.17","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Cor.14.17","label":"","reference":"1 Corinthiens 14:17","prev_osis_id":"1Cor.014.016,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Cor.014.018,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Cor.14.17\" class=\"v\">17<\/sup>Tu rends, il est vrai, d\u2019excellentes actions de gr\u00e2ces, mais l\u2019autre n\u2019est pas \u00e9difi\u00e9.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Cor.14","name":"1 Corinthiens 14","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.14"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Cor.14.18","name":"1 Corinthiens 14:18","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.14.18"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Cor.14.16","name":"1 Corinthiens 14:16","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.14.16"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"18","lastverse":"18","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.14.18","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Cor.14.18","label":"","reference":"1 Corinthiens 14:18","prev_osis_id":"1Cor.014.017,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Cor.014.019,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Cor.14.18\" class=\"v\">18<\/sup>Je rends gr\u00e2ces \u00e0 Dieu de ce que je parle en langue plus que vous tous;<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Cor.14","name":"1 Corinthiens 14","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.14"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Cor.14.19","name":"1 Corinthiens 14:19","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.14.19"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Cor.14.17","name":"1 Corinthiens 14:17","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.14.17"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"19","lastverse":"19","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.14.19","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Cor.14.19","label":"","reference":"1 Corinthiens 14:19","prev_osis_id":"1Cor.014.018,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Cor.014.020,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Cor.14.19\" class=\"v\">19<\/sup>mais, dans l\u2019\u00c9glise, j\u2019aime mieux dire cinq paroles avec mon intelligence, afin d\u2019instruire aussi les autres, que dix mille paroles en langue.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Cor.14","name":"1 Corinthiens 14","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.14"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Cor.14.20","name":"1 Corinthiens 14:20","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.14.20"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Cor.14.18","name":"1 Corinthiens 14:18","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.14.18"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"20","lastverse":"20","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.14.20","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Cor.14.20","label":"","reference":"1 Corinthiens 14:20","prev_osis_id":"1Cor.014.019,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Cor.014.021,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Cor.14.20\" class=\"v\">20<\/sup>Fr\u00e8res, ne soyez pas des enfants sous le rapport du jugement; mais pour la malice, soyez enfants, et, \u00e0 l\u2019\u00e9gard du jugement, soyez des hommes faits.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Cor.14","name":"1 Corinthiens 14","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.14"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Cor.14.21","name":"1 Corinthiens 14:21","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.14.21"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Cor.14.19","name":"1 Corinthiens 14:19","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.14.19"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"21","lastverse":"21","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.14.21","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Cor.14.21","label":"","reference":"1 Corinthiens 14:21","prev_osis_id":"1Cor.014.020,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Cor.014.022,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Cor.14.21\" class=\"v\">21<\/sup>Il est \u00e9crit dans la loi:<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">C\u2019est par des hommes d\u2019une autre langue<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Et par des l\u00e8vres d\u2019\u00e9trangers<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Que je parlerai \u00e0 ce peuple,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Et ils ne m\u2019\u00e9couteront pas m\u00eame ainsi,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">dit le Seigneur.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Cor.14","name":"1 Corinthiens 14","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.14"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Cor.14.22","name":"1 Corinthiens 14:22","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.14.22"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Cor.14.20","name":"1 Corinthiens 14:20","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.14.20"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"22","lastverse":"22","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.14.22","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Cor.14.22","label":"","reference":"1 Corinthiens 14:22","prev_osis_id":"1Cor.014.021,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Cor.014.023,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"m\"><sup id=\"1Cor.14.22\" class=\"v\">22<\/sup>Par cons\u00e9quent, les langues sont un signe, non pour les croyants, mais pour les non-croyants; la proph\u00e9tie, au contraire, est un signe, non pour les non-croyants, mais pour les croyants.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Cor.14","name":"1 Corinthiens 14","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.14"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Cor.14.23","name":"1 Corinthiens 14:23","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.14.23"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Cor.14.21","name":"1 Corinthiens 14:21","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.14.21"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"23","lastverse":"23","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.14.23","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Cor.14.23","label":"","reference":"1 Corinthiens 14:23","prev_osis_id":"1Cor.014.022,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Cor.014.024,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"m\"><sup id=\"1Cor.14.23\" class=\"v\">23<\/sup>Si donc, dans une assembl\u00e9e de l\u2019\u00c9glise enti\u00e8re, tous parlent en langues, et qu\u2019il survienne des hommes du peuple ou des non-croyants, ne diront-ils pas que vous \u00eates fous?<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Cor.14","name":"1 Corinthiens 14","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.14"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Cor.14.24","name":"1 Corinthiens 14:24","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.14.24"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Cor.14.22","name":"1 Corinthiens 14:22","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.14.22"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"24","lastverse":"24","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.14.24","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Cor.14.24","label":"","reference":"1 Corinthiens 14:24","prev_osis_id":"1Cor.014.023,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Cor.014.025,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"m\"><sup id=\"1Cor.14.24\" class=\"v\">24<\/sup>Mais si tous proph\u00e9tisent, et qu\u2019il survienne quelque non-croyant ou un homme du peuple, il est convaincu par tous, il est jug\u00e9 par tous,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Cor.14","name":"1 Corinthiens 14","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.14"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Cor.14.25","name":"1 Corinthiens 14:25","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.14.25"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Cor.14.23","name":"1 Corinthiens 14:23","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.14.23"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"25","lastverse":"25","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.14.25","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Cor.14.25","label":"","reference":"1 Corinthiens 14:25","prev_osis_id":"1Cor.014.024,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Cor.014.026,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"m\"><sup id=\"1Cor.14.25\" class=\"v\">25<\/sup>les secrets de son c\u0153ur sont d\u00e9voil\u00e9s, de telle sorte que, tombant sur sa face, il adorera Dieu, et publiera que Dieu est r\u00e9ellement au milieu de vous.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Cor.14","name":"1 Corinthiens 14","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.14"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Cor.14.26","name":"1 Corinthiens 14:26","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.14.26"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Cor.14.24","name":"1 Corinthiens 14:24","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.14.24"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"26","lastverse":"26","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.14.26","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Cor.14.26","label":"","reference":"1 Corinthiens 14:26","prev_osis_id":"1Cor.014.025,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Cor.014.027,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"m\"><sup id=\"1Cor.14.26\" class=\"v\">26<\/sup>Que faire donc, fr\u00e8res? Lorsque vous vous assemblez, les uns ou les autres parmi vous ont-ils un cantique, une instruction, une r\u00e9v\u00e9lation, une langue, une interpr\u00e9tation, que tout se fasse pour l\u2019\u00e9dification.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Cor.14","name":"1 Corinthiens 14","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.14"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Cor.14.27","name":"1 Corinthiens 14:27","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.14.27"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Cor.14.25","name":"1 Corinthiens 14:25","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.14.25"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"27","lastverse":"27","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.14.27","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Cor.14.27","label":"","reference":"1 Corinthiens 14:27","prev_osis_id":"1Cor.014.026,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Cor.014.028,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"m\"><sup id=\"1Cor.14.27\" class=\"v\">27<\/sup>En est-il qui parlent en langue, que deux ou trois au plus parlent, chacun \u00e0 son tour, et que quelqu\u2019un interpr\u00e8te;<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Cor.14","name":"1 Corinthiens 14","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.14"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Cor.14.28","name":"1 Corinthiens 14:28","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.14.28"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Cor.14.26","name":"1 Corinthiens 14:26","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.14.26"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"28","lastverse":"28","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.14.28","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Cor.14.28","label":"","reference":"1 Corinthiens 14:28","prev_osis_id":"1Cor.014.027,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Cor.014.029,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"m\"><sup id=\"1Cor.14.28\" class=\"v\">28<\/sup>s\u2019il n\u2019y a point d\u2019interpr\u00e8te, qu\u2019on se taise dans l\u2019\u00c9glise, et qu\u2019on parle \u00e0 soi-m\u00eame et \u00e0 Dieu.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Cor.14","name":"1 Corinthiens 14","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.14"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Cor.14.29","name":"1 Corinthiens 14:29","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.14.29"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Cor.14.27","name":"1 Corinthiens 14:27","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.14.27"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"29","lastverse":"29","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.14.29","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Cor.14.29","label":"","reference":"1 Corinthiens 14:29","prev_osis_id":"1Cor.014.028,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Cor.014.030,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"m\"><sup id=\"1Cor.14.29\" class=\"v\">29<\/sup>Pour ce qui est des proph\u00e8tes, que deux ou trois parlent, et que les autres jugent;<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Cor.14","name":"1 Corinthiens 14","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.14"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Cor.14.30","name":"1 Corinthiens 14:30","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.14.30"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Cor.14.28","name":"1 Corinthiens 14:28","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.14.28"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"30","lastverse":"30","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.14.30","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Cor.14.30","label":"","reference":"1 Corinthiens 14:30","prev_osis_id":"1Cor.014.029,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Cor.014.031,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"m\"><sup id=\"1Cor.14.30\" class=\"v\">30<\/sup>et si un autre qui est assis a une r\u00e9v\u00e9lation, que le premier se taise.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Cor.14","name":"1 Corinthiens 14","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.14"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Cor.14.31","name":"1 Corinthiens 14:31","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.14.31"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Cor.14.29","name":"1 Corinthiens 14:29","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.14.29"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"31","lastverse":"31","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.14.31","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Cor.14.31","label":"","reference":"1 Corinthiens 14:31","prev_osis_id":"1Cor.014.030,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Cor.014.032,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"m\"><sup id=\"1Cor.14.31\" class=\"v\">31<\/sup>Car vous pouvez tous proph\u00e9tiser successivement, afin que tous soient instruits et que tous soient exhort\u00e9s.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Cor.14","name":"1 Corinthiens 14","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.14"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Cor.14.32","name":"1 Corinthiens 14:32","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.14.32"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Cor.14.30","name":"1 Corinthiens 14:30","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.14.30"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"32","lastverse":"32","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.14.32","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Cor.14.32","label":"","reference":"1 Corinthiens 14:32","prev_osis_id":"1Cor.014.031,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Cor.014.033,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"m\"><sup id=\"1Cor.14.32\" class=\"v\">32<\/sup>Les esprits des proph\u00e8tes sont soumis aux proph\u00e8tes;<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Cor.14","name":"1 Corinthiens 14","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.14"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Cor.14.33","name":"1 Corinthiens 14:33","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.14.33"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Cor.14.31","name":"1 Corinthiens 14:31","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.14.31"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"33","lastverse":"33","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.14.33","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Cor.14.33","label":"","reference":"1 Corinthiens 14:33","prev_osis_id":"1Cor.014.032,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Cor.014.034,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"m\"><sup id=\"1Cor.14.33\" class=\"v\">33<\/sup>car Dieu n\u2019est pas un Dieu de d\u00e9sordre, mais de paix. Comme dans toutes les \u00c9glises des saints,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Cor.14","name":"1 Corinthiens 14","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.14"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Cor.14.34","name":"1 Corinthiens 14:34","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.14.34"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Cor.14.32","name":"1 Corinthiens 14:32","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.14.32"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"34","lastverse":"34","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.14.34","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Cor.14.34","label":"","reference":"1 Corinthiens 14:34","prev_osis_id":"1Cor.014.033,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Cor.014.035,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"m\"><sup id=\"1Cor.14.34\" class=\"v\">34<\/sup>que les femmes se taisent dans les assembl\u00e9es, car il ne leur est pas permis d\u2019y parler; mais qu\u2019elles soient soumises, selon que le dit aussi la loi.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Cor.14","name":"1 Corinthiens 14","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.14"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Cor.14.35","name":"1 Corinthiens 14:35","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.14.35"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Cor.14.33","name":"1 Corinthiens 14:33","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.14.33"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"35","lastverse":"35","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.14.35","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Cor.14.35","label":"","reference":"1 Corinthiens 14:35","prev_osis_id":"1Cor.014.034,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Cor.014.036,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"m\"><sup id=\"1Cor.14.35\" class=\"v\">35<\/sup>Si elles veulent s\u2019instruire sur quelque chose, qu\u2019elles interrogent leurs maris \u00e0 la maison; car il est mals\u00e9ant \u00e0 une femme de parler dans l\u2019\u00c9glise.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Cor.14","name":"1 Corinthiens 14","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.14"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Cor.14.36","name":"1 Corinthiens 14:36","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.14.36"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Cor.14.34","name":"1 Corinthiens 14:34","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.14.34"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"36","lastverse":"36","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.14.36","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Cor.14.36","label":"","reference":"1 Corinthiens 14:36","prev_osis_id":"1Cor.014.035,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Cor.014.037,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"m\"><sup id=\"1Cor.14.36\" class=\"v\">36<\/sup>Est-ce de chez vous que la parole de Dieu est sortie? Ou est-ce \u00e0 vous seuls qu\u2019elle est parvenue?<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Cor.14","name":"1 Corinthiens 14","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.14"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Cor.14.37","name":"1 Corinthiens 14:37","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.14.37"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Cor.14.35","name":"1 Corinthiens 14:35","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.14.35"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"37","lastverse":"37","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.14.37","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Cor.14.37","label":"","reference":"1 Corinthiens 14:37","prev_osis_id":"1Cor.014.036,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Cor.014.038,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"m\"><sup id=\"1Cor.14.37\" class=\"v\">37<\/sup>Si quelqu\u2019un croit \u00eatre proph\u00e8te ou inspir\u00e9, qu\u2019il reconnaisse que ce que je vous \u00e9cris est un commandement du Seigneur.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Cor.14","name":"1 Corinthiens 14","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.14"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Cor.14.38","name":"1 Corinthiens 14:38","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.14.38"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Cor.14.36","name":"1 Corinthiens 14:36","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.14.36"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"38","lastverse":"38","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.14.38","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Cor.14.38","label":"","reference":"1 Corinthiens 14:38","prev_osis_id":"1Cor.014.037,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Cor.014.039,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"m\"><sup id=\"1Cor.14.38\" class=\"v\">38<\/sup>Et si quelqu\u2019un l\u2019ignore, qu\u2019il l\u2019ignore.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Cor.14","name":"1 Corinthiens 14","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.14"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Cor.14.39","name":"1 Corinthiens 14:39","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.14.39"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Cor.14.37","name":"1 Corinthiens 14:37","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.14.37"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"39","lastverse":"39","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.14.39","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Cor.14.39","label":"","reference":"1 Corinthiens 14:39","prev_osis_id":"1Cor.014.038,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Cor.014.040,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"m\"><sup id=\"1Cor.14.39\" class=\"v\">39<\/sup>Ainsi donc, fr\u00e8res, aspirez au don de proph\u00e9tie, et n\u2019emp\u00eachez pas de parler en langues.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Cor.14","name":"1 Corinthiens 14","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.14"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Cor.14.40","name":"1 Corinthiens 14:40","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.14.40"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Cor.14.38","name":"1 Corinthiens 14:38","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.14.38"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"40","lastverse":"40","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.14.40","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Cor.14.40","label":"","reference":"1 Corinthiens 14:40","prev_osis_id":"1Cor.014.039,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Cor.015.001,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"m\"><sup id=\"1Cor.14.40\" class=\"v\">40<\/sup>Mais que tout se fasse avec biens\u00e9ance et avec ordre.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Cor.14","name":"1 Corinthiens 14","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.14"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Cor.15.1","name":"1 Corinthiens 15:1","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.15.1"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Cor.14.39","name":"1 Corinthiens 14:39","id":"fra-LSG:1Cor.14.39"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"}],"meta":{"fums":"<script>\nvar _BAPI=_BAPI||{};\nif(typeof(_BAPI.t)==='undefined'){\ndocument.write('\\x3Cscript src=\"'+document.location.protocol+'\/\/d2ue49q0mum86x.cloudfront.net\/include\/fums.c.js\"\\x3E\\x3C\/script\\x3E');}\ndocument.write(\"\\x3Cscript\\x3E_BAPI.t('5af81fbe4027a4.25056163');\\x3C\/script\\x3E\");\n<\/script><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/d3a2okcloueqyx.cloudfront.net\/nf1?t=5af81fbe4027a4.25056163\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 0; width: 0;\" \/><\/noscript>","fums_tid":"5af81fbe4027a4.25056163","fums_js_include":"d2ue49q0mum86x.cloudfront.net\/include\/fums.c.js","fums_js":"var _BAPI=_BAPI||{};if(typeof(_BAPI.t)!='undefined'){ _BAPI.t('5af81fbe4027a4.25056163'); }","fums_noscript":"<img src=\"https:\/\/d3a2okcloueqyx.cloudfront.net\/nf1?t=5af81fbe4027a4.25056163\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 0; width: 0;\" \/>"}}}